#    "SFP gets priority when it signals" rule.
#
# 2. FIB-ZONE CONTEXT VETO  — read the rolling 240-bar fib levels and
#    reject momentum/whale longs above fib_0.786 (overextended) and shorts
#    below fib_0.236 (capitulation). This uses fib LEVELS as context only;
#    fast-reactor does NOT fire on SFP itself.
